# Windows 11 Cybersecurity Installation manual - Version Adrian
> This is an installation manual to set up Windows 11 optimized for Cybersecurity work

## Important Links
- Winget Installation packages https://winget.run

## OS Installtion
- Using Newest version of Windows 11 Home (22H2)
- Install all updates
- Uninstall any unnecessary preinstalled software if not installed from disk

## OS Settings
- System power settings -> Screen battery/power 15min/3h - Sleep battery/power 45min/never
- Display scaling -> 100%
- Desktop icons -> small
- Touchpad settings -> Down motion scrolls down
- Default Browser -> Mozilla Firefox
- Personalization -> Set static background and static lockscreen
- Personalization -> Lockscreen Remote "Get fun facts, tips, and more..."
- Personalization -> Color mode dark
- Personalization -> Disable Transparancy effects

Taskbar icons
- Mozilla Firefox
- Google Chrome
- Windows Terminal
- Pycharm
- Notepad

# Microsoft Store
- Install all updates
- Install App Installer (for winget - if not already installed)

# Apps installed by Winget general
winget install -e --id Google.Chrome
winget install -e --id Greenshot.Greenshot
winget install -e --id 7zip.7zip

winget install -e --id Google.Chrome
winget install -e --id Greenshot.Greenshot
winget install -e --id 7zip.7zip

# Apps installed by Winget Cybersecurity
winget install -e --id Insecure.Nmap
winget install -e --id WiresharkFoundation.Wireshark
winget install -e --id PortSwigger.BurpSuite.Community
winget install -e --id brimdata.brim
winget install -e --id Microsoft.VisualStudioCode

winget install -e --id Insecure.Nmap
winget install -e --id WiresharkFoundation.Wireshark
winget install -e --id PortSwigger.BurpSuite.Community
winget install -e --id brimdata.brim
winget install -e --id Microsoft.VisualStudioCode

# App installed by Winget Custom selection
winget install -e --id NordVPN.NordVPN
winget install -e --id Discord.Discord
winget install -e --id Zoom.Zoom
winget install -e --id OpenVPNTechnologies.OpenVPNConnect
winget install -e --id DominikReichl.KeePass
winget install -e --id Spotify.Spotify

